Maintainer: Kosuke Imai <imai@harvard.edu>
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Description: Provides various statistical methods for designing and analyzing two-stage randomized controlled trials.  Two-stage randomized controlled trials can be used to estimate spillover effects as well as direct treatment effects.
